## Goals

The purpose of this tutorial is show you how to build a basic First Person Shooter (FPS) using C++ and Blueprints.

## Objectives

By the end of this tutorial you'll be able to:

* Set-up a Project
* Implement a Character
* Implement a Projectile
* Animate a Character

